<section class="bio h-card">
  <div class="bio-content">
    <img src="/icon.png" alt="Adam Dawkins" class="u-photo" hidden />
    <p>I am a co-founder and the <span class="p-job-title">Technical Director</span> at <a class="p-org" href="https://www.dragondrop.uk">Dragon Drop</a>, a development agency focused on building bespoke internal tools for organisations that want to use technology that works for them.</p>
    <p>I've been a developer since 2008, and most days, we're using Ruby on Rails.</p>
    <p>This is where I write about things.</p>
    <!-- Hidden h-card properties -->
    <span class="p-name" hidden>Adam Dawkins</span>
    <a class="u-url u-uid" href="https://adamdawkins.com/" hidden>https://adamdawkins.com/</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Recent Articles</h2>
